These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
3 different games are played: scrabble, poker, billiard
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, rabbit
House: victorian, wooden, townhouse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, zombie, thriller
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, august, march
City: rome, prague, new-york
 1. the person traveling to rome is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the person traveling to new-york is the townhouse house##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the wooden house is the person playing billiard##1
 6. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the wooden house##1
10. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Game          | poker       | billiard    | scrabble         |
| Pet         | horse    | rabbit  | fish        |
| House           | victorian | wooden   | townhouse      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie        | thriller    | crime       |
| Birthday   | august     | january  | march       |
| City         | rome     | prague | new-york |

