The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, puzzles, gardening
 1. the person traveling to miami is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is the person who growslily##1
 3. the person who growslily is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 8. the vegafina-smoker is the person who growsiris##1
 9. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
