 6. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 7. the person driving the skateboard is the gothic-revival house##1
 8. the person who likes mauve is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is between the person who likes mauve and the person who likes blue##2
10. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
