There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, mauve, grey
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, polish
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, bolivar, cain
3 different games are played: billiard, bridge, monopoly
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, may, july
 1. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of jazz is in the middle##1
 3. the polish is on the right of the victorian house##1
 4. the tower house is the person who likes mauve##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is between the fan of blues and the american##2
 8. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the cain-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | blues | jazz      | classical      |
| House         | victorian     | palace     | tower  |
| Color   | grey | chestnut  | mauve |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | polish     | american |
| Cigar           | dannemann        | cain | bolivar     |
| Game         | billiard    | monopoly | bridge   |
| Birthday     | may        | july        | march   |

