.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, soul, funk
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, aconite
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, swisher, bluemaster
3 different games are played: domino, whist, mah-jongg
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, d&bsy, mystery
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, july, may
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, emerald, lavender
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person playing domino##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person watching epic movies and the person playing whist##2
5. the person who growsaconite is between the person playing mah-jongg and the bluemaster-smoker##2
6. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the fan of soul##1
8. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the fan of funk##1
9. the person watching d&bsy movies is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre      | d&b      | soul      | funk       |
| Flower          | iris      | aconite    | tulip   |
| Cigar         | bluemaster    | game     | swisher     |
| Game           | whist    | domino | mah-jongg   |
| Movie-Genre   | d&bsy    | mystery    | epic       |
| Birthday         | may | april      | july    |
| Color     | emerald       | chestnut | lavender |

