.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, videographer, doctor
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, baccarat, bluemaster
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, thai, argentine
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, canasta
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, tulip, lily
House: art-deco, tower, gothic-revival
1. the tower house is the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the right of the chinese##1
3. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
4. the argentine is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the videographer is between the person drinking fanta and the oliveros-smoker##2
6. the doctor is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person playing whist##1
8. the art-deco house is the argentine##1
9. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | fanta       | coffee     | cola         |
| Job          | accountant     | videographer      | doctor     |
| Cigar         | baccarat | bluemaster    | oliveros      |
| Nationality   | chinese   | thai | argentine    |
| Game   | whist        | canasta     | bridge   |
| Flower         | sunflower     | tulip | lily |
| House     | tower     | gothic-revival       | art-deco    |

