.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different games are played: poker, billiard, monopoly
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, traveling, drawing
City: colone, venice, hannover
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, daffodil, dahlia
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rabbit
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, chaman, oliveros
House: art-deco, tower, palace
1. the person playing poker is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the palace house is the cain-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to colone is between the person playing monopoly and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the palace house##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
6. the tower house is on the left of the palace house##1
7. the person traveling to venice is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the art-deco house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Game      | billiard    | poker       | monopoly      |
| Hobby          | cooking   | drawing   | traveling  |
| City           | venice  | colone | hannover    |
| Flower   | aconite   | daffodil     | dahlia  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog        | hedgehog |
| Cigar         | chaman | cain   | oliveros  |
| House     | tower    | palace     | art-deco      |

 